    <patterns>
      <pattern name="Validation ordering" location="spec FR-32">
        New order: schema validity → executor existence (Choice value in `sprk_playbookexecutortype`) → executor-specific typed config (FR-16 schema) → Action template contract (if applicable) → cross-field invariants.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Wave 3 typed config schema endpoint" location="src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/">
        Each executor's `GetConfigSchema()` returns a TypeScript-like schema DTO. The validate skill calls the BFF endpoint to fetch + validate node config against the appropriate schema.
      </pattern>
